{
  "texts": [
    "IC could play a larger part in driving content capture.",
    "For example, more research in optimizing shot composition for anticipating events would be of benefit.",
    "There may also be interest in stylized shot compositions that present in-game events, for instance, using cinematic style transfer (Wang et al. 2023) to emphasize praiseworthy shots.",
    "Perhaps one day we may be able to watch a sports game in a Tarantio-esque style.",
    "Similar to many other applications of IC, the problem landscape for UAV-based cinematography is generally poorly defined (Mademlis et al. 2018a)."
  ]
}